response.original_title: Ultraseven - From Another Planet with Love
response.overview: From Another Planet with Love (遊星より愛をこめて, Yūsei Yori Ai wo Komete) is the banned twelfth episode of Ultraseven. Although it aired in 1967 without issue, the episode has not been rereleased since 1970, with the exception of its inclusion in the CINAR English dub in 1994, where it was called Crystalized Corpuscles.
